Metorex Says Copper Mineral Reserve Increase by 3%, Sees More Improvements

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-04-04T05:24:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-04/metorex-says-copper-mineral-reserve-increase-by-3-sees-more-improvements.html
Metorex Ltd. (MTX)  said its copper mineral
reserves have increased by 3 percent and that continued
extensions and drilling at Ruashi will continue in fiscal 2011.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
